## Technical Stack:
- **Frontend**: Next.js 14 + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend**: Supabase (Database + Auth + Storage + Real-time)
- **AI**: Groq API (6000 tokens/day free tier)
- **Deploy**: Vercel
- **Payment**: Manual credit system (no Stripe)
- **State Management**: Zustand
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod

## Database Schema:
- users (extends auth.users)
- credits (wallet balance)
- credit_logs (transaction history)
- credit_requests (loan requests)
- decorations (themes/customization)
- posts (social content)
- workspaces (team collaboration)
- tasks (AI-powered task management)
- achievements (gamification)
- activity_logs (user tracking)

