## Key Features:
- AI-powered task management with Groq
- Gamification with XP and achievements
- Social collaboration with workspaces
- Time tracking with Pomodoro timer
- Bilingual support (EN/TH)
- Manual credit wallet system
- Real-time updates
- Advanced admin dashboard 